name: HoYeon Jung
description: HoYeon Jung is a South Korean model and actress who became a global star for her role in the Netflix series "Squid Game." She is known for her fiery red hair and has worked as a Louis Vuitton ambassador. Her performance in "Squid Game" earned her critical acclaim and several awards, including a Screen Actors Guild Award and a Primetime Emmy nomination.
